Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.91,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\bord0\shad0\c&H7A7674&\b0\frz358.7\pos(554.666,229.733)}瞳美  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.91,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\bord0\shad0\c&H7A7674&\b0\frz357.7\pos(497.066,444.133)}是瞳美啊  歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.83,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\bord0\shad0\c&H7A7674&\b0\frz358.1\pos(511.999,197.866)}請多指教  瞳美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.83,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\bord0\shad0\c&H7A7674&\b0\frz358.1\pos(556.799,256.399)}人都齊了  來談今年辦野營過夜的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.83,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\bord0\shad0\c&H7A7674&\b0\pos(525.866,301.199)\frz358.1}社長好認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.83,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\bord0\shad0\c&H7A7674&\b0\frz357.7\pos(509.866,345.999)}千草少廢話！！！
